Graphical PMI Viewer

  • The graphical PMI visualization was generated by the NIST STEP File Analyzer and Viewer and displayed with X3DOM. The graphical PMI is from a STEP file generated from one of the NIST CAD models.
  • Use the mouse in 'Examine' mode to rotate, pan, and zoom. Use Page Down to switch between perspective and orthographic views.
